is it called hair spray.

06:47.407 --> 06:48.908
Just simply Control.

06:48.908 --> 06:51.410
And the words "for men"
are written about 37 times

06:51.411 --> 06:52.912
all over the goddamn can.

06:52.912 --> 06:55.364
Hm. And it's called
butch assurance.

06:55.364 --> 06:56.448
Still hair spray,

06:56.449 --> 06:58.250
no matter if
they call it "Balls."

06:59.535 --> 07:02.120
It's all on your very own shelf,
which is to be labeled

07:02.121 --> 07:03.922
"Donald's Saturday Night
Douche Kit."

07:06.592 --> 07:08.677
By the way, are you
spending the night?

07:08.678 --> 07:10.429
Nope. I'm driving back.

07:11.931 --> 07:13.632
Why didn't the prick
call you and cancel?

07:13.633 --> 07:15.551
Suppose you'd driven
all this way for nothing?

07:15.551 --> 07:17.769
Why do you keep
calling him a prick?

07:17.770 --> 07:20.355
Whoever heard of an analyst
having a session with a patient

07:20.356 --> 07:22.808
for two hours
on Saturday evening.

07:22.809 --> 07:24.727
He simply prefers
to take Mondays off.

07:24.727 --> 07:27.813
Works late Saturdays
and takes Mondays off?

07:27.814 --> 07:30.449
What is he, a psychiatrist
or a hairdresser?

07:30.450 --> 07:31.534
Well, actually, he's both.

07:31.534 --> 07:34.370
He shrinks my head
and then combs me out.

07:34.370 --> 07:36.622
Besides, I had to
come in town

07:36.622 --> 07:37.623
to a birthday
party anyway.

07:37.623 --> 07:39.625
Right?
You had to remind me.

07:41.127 --> 07:42.628
If there's one thing
I'm not ready for,

07:42.628 --> 07:46.131
it's five screaming queens
singing "Happy Birthday."

07:46.132 --> 07:47.633
Who's coming?

07:47.633 --> 07:49.468
Well, they're really
all Harold's friends.

07:49.469 --> 07:51.304
It's his birthday,
and I want everything to be

07:51.304 --> 07:52.805
just the way he'd want it.

07:52.805 --> 07:54.807
I don't wanna have to
listen to him kvetch about how

07:54.807 --> 07:56.308
"Nobody ever does anything

07:56.309 --> 07:57.893
for anybody but themselves."

07:57.894 --> 07:59.478
"Himself."

07:59.479 --> 08:00.480
Himself.

08:01.981 --> 08:03.482
I think you know
everybody anyway.

08:04.650 --> 08:06.151
It's the same old
tired fairies

08:06.152 --> 08:07.653
you've seen around
since the day one.

08:09.155 --> 08:13.025
Actually, there'll be seven,
counting Harold and you. And me.

08:13.025 --> 08:16.495
Are you calling me a screaming
queen or a tired fairy?

08:16.496 --> 08:18.581
I beg your pardon.

08:18.581 --> 08:20.583
There'll be six tired,
screaming fairy queens

08:20.583 --> 08:22.001
and one anxious queer.

08:24.921 --> 08:26.372
Listen, I'll be out of
your way in one second.

08:26.372 --> 08:29.208
I've just got
one more thing to do here.

08:29.208 --> 08:31.460
Surgery, so early
in the evening?

08:31.460 --> 08:32.544
"Cunt."

08:33.546 --> 08:35.014
That's French, with a cedilla.

08:35.965 --> 08:37.967
I just have to
comb my hair again.

08:37.967 --> 08:39.434
