of deception.

08:54.784 --> 08:56.819
My hairline
starts about here.

08:56.819 --> 08:58.904
All this is just
tortured forward.

08:58.905 --> 09:01.407
Well, I hope for your sake,
no strong wind comes up.

09:02.825 --> 09:05.327
Well, if one does,
I'll be in terrible trouble.

09:05.328 --> 09:09.248
