and shoulder-length fringe.

09:09.248 --> 09:10.832
Look.

09:10.833 --> 09:12.334
Not good, huh?

09:12.335 --> 09:14.303
Hm. Not the greatest.
Tsk.

09:14.303 --> 09:15.671
It's called getting old.

09:18.007 --> 09:20.509
Well, there's one thing
to be said for masturbation:

09:20.509 --> 09:22.477
