look your best.

09:22.478 --> 09:24.012
Oh. Will you get
out of here?

09:28.684 --> 09:30.769
What are you
so depressed about?

09:30.770 --> 09:32.822
Other than the usual
everything, I mean.

09:32.822 --> 09:35.274
I really don't wanna
get into it.

09:35.274 --> 09:36.608
Well, if you're
not gonna tell me,

09:36.609 --> 09:38.827
