a conversation in-depth?

09:38.828 --> 09:41.163
A warm, rewarding,
meaningful friendship?

09:41.163 --> 09:42.998
Up yours!

09:42.999 --> 09:45.501
Why, Captain Butler, how you talk.

09:45.501 --> 09:47.419
It's just that, today,
I finally realized

09:47.420 --> 09:49.922
