to be a failure.

09:49.922 --> 09:52.174
I was groomed for it.

09:52.174 --> 09:54.759
Naturally, it all goes
back to Evelyn and Walt.

09:54.760 --> 09:56.762
Christ. How sick analysts
must get of hearing

09:56.762 --> 09:59.631
