they're paid for.

11:28.220 --> 11:30.605
Oh, that is, how you say,
your neurosis.

11:30.606 --> 11:34.192
I'm a spoiled brat. So, what
do I know about maturity?

11:36.145 --> 11:38.197
The only thing "mature" means
to me is Victor Mature.

11:39.615 --> 11:42.150
I can understand people having
an affinity for the stage,

11:42.151 --> 11:45.287
