who can take them seriously?

11:45.287 --> 11:48.323
Well, I'm sorry if
your sense of art is offended.

11:48.324 --> 11:49.875
Odd as it may seem,

11:49.875 --> 11:53.078
there was no Shubert Theatre
in Hot Coffee, Mississippi.

11:53.079 --> 11:55.664
However, thanks to
the silver screen,

11:55.664 --> 11:58.667
your neurosis has got...style.

11:58.667 --> 12:00.168
It takes a certain flair

12:00.169 --> 12:03.672
to squander one's unemployment
check at Pavilion.

12:03.672 --> 12:06.257
What's so snappy about being
head over heels in debt?

12:07.760 --> 12:09.762
The only thing smart about it
is the ingenious ways

12:09.762 --> 12:11.764
I dodge the bill collectors.

12:13.015 --> 12:14.516
Come to think of it,
you're the type

12:14.517 --> 12:16.602
