a bad name.

12:16.602 --> 12:18.687
And you, Donald...

12:18.687 --> 12:21.189
you are a credit
to the homosexual.

12:21.190 --> 12:22.691
A reliable, hardworking,

12:22.691 --> 12:24.192
floor-scrubbing,

12:24.193 --> 12:27.246
bill-paying fag, who don't
owe nothin' to nobody.

12:27.246 --> 12:29.031
I am a model fairy.

12:30.282 --> 12:31.783
You think it's just nifty...

12:31.784 --> 12:34.286
how I've always flitted
from Beverly Hills

12:34.286 --> 12:37.839
to Rome to Acapulco
to Amsterdam...

12:37.840 --> 12:40.542
picking up a lot of
one night stands.

12:40.543 --> 12:43.629
And a lot of custom-made duds
along the trail.

12:46.132 --> 12:47.633
Well, I'm here to tell you

12:47.633 --> 12:49.635
