in all those miles--

12:49.635 --> 12:52.554
The only place I've ever been
happy was on the goddamn plane.

12:54.774 --> 12:57.693
Run, charge,
run.

12:57.693 --> 12:59.277
Borrow, make.

13:01.280 --> 13:04.783
Spend...run.

13:08.120 --> 13:10.071
