for yourself, is there?

13:44.907 --> 13:46.408
Nothing.

13:47.910 --> 13:49.912
I adore cheap sentiment.

14:11.133 --> 14:13.135
Backstage, New Moon.

14:14.637 --> 14:17.139
Alan. My God!
I don't believe it.

14:17.139 --> 14:18.440
