no good for me.

14:24.813 --> 14:25.814
Oh, I'm all tied up too,

14:25.814 --> 14:27.315
but I...

14:27.316 --> 14:29.117
I thought I might just
drop by for a drink?

14:29.952 --> 14:31.453
Oh, you mean now?

14:32.955 --> 14:34.456
Oh, um...

14:34.456 --> 14:37.959
well, Alan,
old buddy, um...

14:37.960 --> 14:39.461
well, you see,
it's a friend's birthday,

14:39.461 --> 14:41.463
and I'm having some people in.

14:42.965 --> 14:44.466
