Say that again,

48:28.405 --> 48:30.824
and I won't have to take
my appetite depressant.

48:30.824 --> 48:32.492
All right, up the steps,
to the john. Right?

48:32.492 --> 48:35.077
Easy does it.
One step at a time.

48:37.531 --> 48:40.116
