50:01.448 --> 50:03.450
I'm starved, Em.

50:03.450 --> 50:05.535
I'm ready for some of your

50:05.535 --> 50:08.955
Alice B. Toklas
opium-baked lasagna.

50:08.955 --> 50:12.041
Are you really?
Oh, that makes me so happy.

50:12.042 --> 50:14.427
Maybe I'll just
serve before I leave.

50:14.428 --> 50:16.012
Nobody's
going anywhere.

50:16.013 --> 50:18.515
You are going to have
<i>schmertz</i> tomorrow

50:18.515 --> 50:21.518
you wouldn't believe.
Do a figure eight on that.

50:22.686 --> 50:25.188
I'm turning on,
and you're just turning.

50:25.188 --> 50:27.106
Michael, is there
any air spray?

50:27.107 --> 50:29.692
