to be holding his head,

50:29.693 --> 50:31.111
not doing his hair.

50:31.111 --> 50:32.946
"Air" spray. Not hair spray.

50:32.946 --> 50:35.148
There's a can of floral spray
right on top of the john.

50:35.148 --> 50:36.232
Right. Thanks.

50:37.784 --> 50:40.870
I keep my grass
in the medicine cabinet,

50:40.871 --> 50:41.872
in the Band-Aid
box.

50:43.373 --> 50:45.875
Somebody told me
it's the safest place.

50:45.876 --> 50:47.377
If the cops arrive,

50:47.377 --> 50:48.878
