in the bathroom

50:48.879 --> 50:51.164
and flush it down the john.

50:51.164 --> 50:52.632
Very cagey.

50:52.632 --> 50:55.217
Makes more sense
than where I was keeping it:

50:55.218 --> 50:58.221
in an oregano jar
in the spice rack.

51:00.090 --> 51:01.674
I kept forgetting
and accidentally

51:01.675 --> 51:05.178
