with the salad. Hm.

51:05.178 --> 51:06.679
But I think she liked it.

51:06.680 --> 51:09.182
No matter what meal
she comes over for,

51:09.182 --> 51:10.683
even if it's breakfast,
she says:

51:10.684 --> 51:12.185
