and say things like,

51:19.659 --> 51:21.077
"Hot enough for you?"

51:21.078 --> 51:24.164
I don't use the steam room
when I go to the gym.

51:24.164 --> 51:27.116
It's bad for you after
a workout. Flattens you down.

51:27.117 --> 51:29.702
Just after you've broken
your back to blow yourself up.

51:29.703 --> 51:32.455
Like a poisoned dog.

51:32.456 --> 51:33.507
Yeah.

51:34.458 --> 51:36.460
Oh, Harold,
he's beautiful.

51:36.460 --> 51:39.463
Yeah. Beautiful.

51:39.463 --> 51:42.466
He has unnatural
natural beauty.

51:43.467 --> 51:45.852
Not that
that means anything.

51:45.852 --> 51:47.353
It doesn't mean everything.

51:47.354 --> 51:51.107
Keep telling yourself that as
your hair drops out in handfuls.

51:51.108 --> 51:53.193
Faggots are worse than
women about their age.

51:53.193 --> 51:56.196
They think their lives
are over at 30.

51:56.196 --> 51:58.448
Physical beauty is not
all that goddamn important.

51:58.448 --> 52:00.533
Of course not,
how could it be?

52:00.534 --> 52:02.819
It's only in the eye
of the beholder.

52:04.204 --> 52:05.622
And it's only skin deep.

52:07.073 --> 52:09.575
Only skin deep.

52:09.576 --> 52:11.578
And it's transitory too.

52:11.578 --> 52:14.047
It's terribly transitory.

52:15.632 --> 52:20.219
Oh, yes. It's too bad about
this poor boy's face.

52:21.221 --> 52:22.722
It's tragic.

52:22.722 --> 52:25.508
He's absolutely cursed.

52:26.810 --> 52:31.264
How could his beauty
ever compare with my soul?

52:31.264 --> 52:33.849
And although
I've never seen my soul,

52:33.850 --> 52:36.352
I understand
from my mother's rabbi

52:36.353 --> 52:37.737
that it's a knockout.

52:37.737 --> 52:41.690
I, however, cannot seem
to locate it for a gander.

52:41.691 --> 52:44.193
And if I could...

52:44.194 --> 52:47.197
