52:47.197 --> 52:50.200
for some skin-deep,
transitory,

52:50.200 --> 52:51.951
meaningless beauty.

52:51.952 --> 52:54.537
Forgive him, father,
for he know not what he do.

52:55.755 --> 52:59.258
Michael, you don't know what
side of the fence you're on.

52:59.259 --> 53:02.262
Say something pro-religion,
you're against it.

53:02.262 --> 53:05.265
