against that.

53:05.265 --> 53:08.768
One might say you have
some problem in that area.

53:08.768 --> 53:11.270
You can't live with it,
and you can't live without it.

53:11.271 --> 53:12.772
Hot stuff coming through.

53:12.772 --> 53:15.524
One could murder you
with very little effort.

53:15.525 --> 53:18.110
You hang on to that
great insurance policy

53:18.111 --> 53:19.362
called the Church.

53:19.362 --> 53:21.447
That's right.
I believe in God.

53:21.448 --> 53:25.201
And if it turns out there
isn't one, okay, nothing's lost.

53:25.202 --> 53:27.370
