54:03.523 --> 54:05.358
Bread. Isn't that great?

54:05.358 --> 54:08.361
Emory, it looks
absolutely fabulous.

54:08.361 --> 54:10.279
I'd make somebody
a good wife.

54:10.280 --> 54:14.000
I could cook. I could
do an apartment and, um...

54:14.000 --> 54:16.002
