54:16.002 --> 54:18.454
Kiss me quick, I'm Carmen.

54:20.924 --> 54:24.010
One really needs castanets
for that sort of thing.

54:24.010 --> 54:25.711
And a getaway car.

54:25.712 --> 54:27.296
