55:22.602 --> 55:25.187
I hear that if you puts a knife under the bed,

55:25.188 --> 55:27.406
it cuts the pain.

55:27.407 --> 55:28.991
I hear if you put
a knife under your chin,

55:28.992 --> 55:30.777
