dissolved into Flo Nightingale.

55:39.202 --> 55:40.786
Ladies and gentlemen.

55:40.787 --> 55:42.672
Oh, correction.

55:42.672 --> 55:44.757
Ladies and ladies.

55:44.758 --> 55:46.760
