57:05.371 --> 57:06.872
When the truth is,
you're not fatter

57:06.873 --> 57:08.457
and no thinner
than you ever are.

57:08.458 --> 57:09.509
Polly Paranoia.

57:10.460 --> 57:12.128
Just great, Emory.
Thank you.

57:12.128 --> 57:15.214
Connie Casserole,
no trouble at all.

57:15.215 --> 57:16.633
Oh, Mary, don't ask.

57:16.633 --> 57:18.551
And this
pathological lateness.

57:18.551 --> 57:20.135
It's downright
crazy.

57:20.136 --> 57:21.554
Turning.

57:21.554 --> 57:25.057
